OL,3,CFootball club insist striker remains
OL,4,Ctheirs despite signing for another club
OL,6,FFC Halifax Town say that footballer
OL,7,FWill Harris remains their player,
OL,8,Fimmediately after Hartlepool United
OL,9,Fannounced his transfer.
OL,11,FThe striker was unveiled at
OL,12,FHartlepool's stadium today (Saturday
OL,13,F27 June), only for FC Halifax to put
OL,14,Fout a statement minutes later.
OL,16,FIt reads: "Contrary to a recent
OL,17,Fannouncement from another party, FC
OL,18,FHalifax Town can confirm it holds the
OL,19,Fplayer registration for player, Will
OL,20,FHarris.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
