OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1782731897
OL,3,CFootball club insist striker remains
OL,4,Ctheirs despite signing for another club
OL,6,F"A one year option was exercised for
OL,7,Fan additional contract year, for which
OL,8,Fthe player has been informed within
OL,9,Fthe normal administrative process of
OL,10,Fthe FA and importantly within the FA
OL,11,Ftimescale for 2026."
OL,13,FIn the transfer announcement, the
OL,14,Fplayer said: "I'm delighted to be here
OL,15,F(at Hartlepool).
OL,17,F"I'm looking forward to getting back
OL,18,Fin next week, meeting the lads and
OL,19,Fgetting straight to work in pre-
OL,20,Fseason."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
