OL,3,CFootball club insist striker remains
OL,4,Ctheirs despite signing for another club
OL,6,FIn their announcement, Hartlepool say:
OL,7,F"The 25-year-old striker has agreed a
OL,8,Ftwo-year contract at Victoria Park
OL,9,Funtil June 2028, with the Club holding
OL,10,Fan option to extend the agreement by a
OL,11,Ffurther year through to June 2029.
OL,13,F"The deal is subject to the relevant
OL,14,Fapprovals."
OL,16,FITV Calendar has approached Hartlepool
OL,17,FUnited for a response.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/3
